373
00:32:59,911 --> 00:33:02,551
<i>Now, future reading!</i>

374
00:33:09,087 --> 00:33:14,230
<i>You will become a
Chiranjeevi in the time to come</i>

375
00:33:15,760 --> 00:33:23,235
<i>You will dance like Chiranjeevi!
