381
00:33:54,799 --> 00:34:01,614
<i>What should we do for that?</i>

382
00:34:02,140 --> 00:34:07,783
<i>Do pranks!
Don't disturb others!</i>

383
00:34:08,980 --> 00:34:14,623
<i>Always smile
Don't make others laugh at you!</i>

384
00:34:15,787 --> 00:34:21,965
<i>Dream yourself and don't
forget to make your dreams real</i>

385
00:34:22,593 --> 00:34:28,305
<i>Prosper, but don't forget
the land from where you took off!</i>

386
00:34:28,499 --> 00:34:35,644
<i>Don't forget Motherland and Mother India</i>

387
00:34:37,175 --> 00:34:42,175
Volga

