391
00:35:37,869 --> 00:35:40,372
Big Mountain (Penu konda),
Golkonda, Anaconda!

392
00:35:40,838 --> 00:35:41,873
Rattle snake!

393
00:35:43,474 --> 00:35:46,182
- Is goddess angry? -You are
having some bad thoughts in your mind!

394
00:35:46,310 --> 00:35:48,290
