any other bad thought in my mind!

395
00:35:48,412 --> 00:35:49,390
That is bad!

396
00:35:50,248 --> 00:35:53,195
- Shall I try it once again?
- No, once in a day! I know that!

397
00:35:53,417 --> 00:35:55,897
